Name: Songs that contain other songs
Description:
Not samples but a prominent riff, melody, hook, etc. that sound exactly like another song in your song.

it could be:
- a song “quoting” another song (music or even lyrics)
- a song with a riff that you realize was later stolen for another song
- songs that share chord progressions
and more

Name: You _Probably_ Haven't Heard Of Them Again
Description:
But this time with a minimum of 250,000 monthly listeners! 

i.e. a really successful band that you think we've still somehow not heard of.

Voting rules: okay if you’ve heard of the band but if you’ve heard songs by the band, give it no votes.
